{#-
  Telegram MarkdownV2 report layout (spec: notifier-telegram §需求 结构化布局).
  Structure: 抬头(非 intent) → 覆盖行 → 根因分析(置顶) → 发现(四元组去重 +
  severity 降序 + 来源) → 健康态. Multi-target findings section by host when
  distinct(non-None target_name) > 1; single-host degrades to flat list.
  Every dynamic value passes through `mdv2_escape`; `*` / `↳` / `·` are
  structural / literal glyphs the truncation balancer accounts for.
-#}
